S=input("enter any word you like(in lower case):")
s = len(S)
a=S.count('a')
e=S.count('e')
i=S.count('i')
o=S.count('o')
u=S.count('u')
d=a+e+i+o+u
print("the total number of letters")
print(s)
print("the total number of vowels")
print(d)
print("the total number of consonants")
print(s-d)
output

enter any word you like(in lower case):akshika
the total number of letters
7
the total number of vowels
3
the total number of consonants
4
